.DT
refresh
Discworld player help
refresh

.SH Name
.SI 5
refresh - Refresh your character.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
refresh totally
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Refresh will erase your character and recreate it.  It will be like
you're logging in for the first time, ie no money, no equipment, no skills,
no quests, no family, no clubs, no nothing.  You will appear back in the
foyer of the newbie area, with the usual newbie equipment.

%^YELLOW%^Use with care and note that any attempt to recover your equipment is
considered cheating.%^RESET%^
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> refresh totally
%^BOLD%^WARNING!  This will restart your character.%^RESET%^

Are you sure you wish to refresh yourself totally?
> y
Ok, refreshing totally.
Doing refresh...
Done refreshing.
You reappear in a more solid form.
.EI

.SH See also
.SI 5
score, skills.
.EI
